<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets...</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:36.343 --> 00:07:36.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>they were here.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:38.103 --> 00:07:38.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They spoke to me.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:39.423 --> 00:07:41.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You had a vision, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We saw nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:42.081 --> 00:07:42.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did they say?</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:43.081 --> 00:07:45.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>They mentioned something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about a Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:45.365 --> 00:07:46.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that a part of some prophecy?</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:47.020 --> 00:07:48.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not one that I know of.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:49.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:50.362 --> 00:07:51.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Jake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be leaving soon.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:52.879 --> 00:07:56.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have got to find out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what those inscriptions say.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:57.757 --> 00:07:59.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish we could translate them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more quickly</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:59.836 --> 00:08:01.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we don't have the resources.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:01.876 --> 00:08:03.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fortunately, we do.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:08.154 --> 00:08:11.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a pretty good idea what this was</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the minute I laid eyes on it.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:12.873 --> 00:08:13.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That confirms it.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:14.697 --> 00:08:16.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a slab of stone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with some writing on it.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:16.430 --> 00:08:17.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax...</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:18.310 --> 00:08:20.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want me to say, Benjamin?</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:21.110 --> 00:08:23.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not picking up any</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>residual energy readings--</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:23.590 --> 00:08:26.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>certainly nothing that would explain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how it threw you across the room.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:27.008 --> 00:08:29.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to translate the inscriptions.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:30.247 --> 00:08:32.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was afraid you were going to say that.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:34.367 --> 00:08:36.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Ranjen's translation program.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:36.565 --> 00:08:38.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not complete,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but at least it's a start.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:39.884 --> 00:08:41.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:46.842 --> 00:08:47.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:48.842 --> 00:08:50.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chimes jingling )</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:50.121 --> 00:08:51.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>CLERGYMAN: Services are about to begin.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:58.919 --> 00:09:01.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, services are about to begin.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:05.596 --> 00:09:06.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Ops to Captain Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:07.196 --> 00:09:07.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:08.358 --> 00:09:10.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>We just received</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a communication from Bajor.</i></c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:10.684 --> 00:09:12.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kai Winn is on her way to the station.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:27.770 --> 00:09:30.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Welcome to Deep Space Nine, Your Eminence.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:30.409 --> 00:09:31.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:32.329 --> 00:09:33.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What brings you to the station?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:33.988 --> 00:09:35.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should think that would be clear.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:36.387 --> 00:09:39.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You removed an artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from an archaeological site</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:39.389 --> 00:09:41.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>without consulting the Vedek Assembly.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:42.426 --> 00:09:43.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant no disrespect.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:43.905 --> 00:09:47.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how we would be sensitive to such matters.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:48.450 --> 00:09:49.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>During the Occupation,</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:49.671 --> 00:09:52.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Cardassians plundered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor's historical treasures</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:52.759 --> 00:09:54.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as if it were their right.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:54.962 --> 00:09:57.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never imagined that you would behave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in such a manner.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:58.527 --> 00:10:00.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you that the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be returned</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:00.888 --> 00:10:02.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as soon as I've finished studying it.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:02.939 --> 00:10:06.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was not aware that you had</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>expertise in Bajoran history.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:06.498 --> 00:10:09.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then why not leave the artifact</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:09.280 --> 00:10:10.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the hands of those who do?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:11.257 --> 00:10:12.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are scholars on Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:12.898 --> 00:10:15.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>who've devoted their lives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the study of such things.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:10:16.335 --> 00:10:18.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand, but I brought it here</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:10:18.675 --> 00:10:20.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because I believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's what the Prophets want.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:21.114 --> 00:10:22.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:22.394 --> 00:10:25.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I take it this has something to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with your vision?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:26.252 --> 00:10:26.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:28.691 --> 00:10:29.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:29.772 --> 00:10:32.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I-I didn't realize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the Prophets told you</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:32.651 --> 00:10:33.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bring the relic here.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:35.050 --> 00:10:36.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, they didn't... not in so many words.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:37.040 --> 00:10:38.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:39.188 --> 00:10:40.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then exactly what did they say?</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:42.067 --> 00:10:43.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:43.607 --> 00:10:44.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's difficult to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:46.226 --> 00:10:47.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets are not always clear.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:48.726 --> 00:10:51.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, since they have never spoken to me</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:51.924 --> 00:10:53.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to take your word for it.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:54.764 --> 00:10:57.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I know is, for now, it belongs here.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:59.522 --> 00:11:02.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who am I to argue</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Emissary of the Prophets?</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:11:09.759 --> 00:11:13.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And then she contacted Starfleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and lodged a formal protest.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:14.558 --> 00:11:16.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that why Admiral Ross</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted to talk to you?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:17.677 --> 00:11:18.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, how'd it go?</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:19.257 --> 00:11:21.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He told me to stop meddling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in Bajoran affairs</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:21.658 --> 00:11:23.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and return the damn tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:23.955 --> 00:11:26.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know how Starfleet feels</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about this Emissary thing.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:27.194 --> 00:11:29.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It makes them very uncomfortable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've allowed the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:30.034 --> 00:11:32.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to view you as a religious icon.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:33.253 --> 00:11:34.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It used to make you uncomfortable, too.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:35.692 --> 00:11:36.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:37.651 --> 00:11:40.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess the Prophets have spoken to me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one too many times.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:41.270 --> 00:11:43.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember when you used</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to call them "wormhole aliens."</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:44.289 --> 00:11:47.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wormhole aliens or Prophets...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it really doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:48.128 --> 00:11:51.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The fact is, they exist out of time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and over the centuries</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:52.027 --> 00:11:54.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've given the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>glimpses of the future</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:54.766 --> 00:11:56.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>glimpses that the Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have written down</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:56.767 --> 00:11:58.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to help them guide succeeding generations.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:58.765 --> 00:12:03.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If whatever is written here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can help me avoid mistakes</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:03.470 --> 00:12:06.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>can help me make the right decisions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then I'd be a fool to ignore it.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:07.182 --> 00:12:09.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fair enough, but if you don't mind</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:09.744 --> 00:12:12.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to continue to think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of them as wormhole aliens.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:14.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I know is...</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:15.320 --> 00:12:18.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that they have a relationship with Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:18.939 --> 00:12:20.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that stretches back over a thousand years.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:21.358 --> 00:12:23.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They care what happens to Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:23.838 --> 00:12:26.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They proved that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when they kept the Dominion fleet</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:26.039 --> 00:12:27.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:27.376 --> 00:12:28.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't you have to talk them into it?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:29.956 --> 00:12:33.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Didn't they say they would exact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some kind of penance for helping you?</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:33.974 --> 00:12:35.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but they listened,</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:36.733 --> 00:12:39.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they saved Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the rest of the Alpha Quadrant.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:39.792 --> 00:12:42.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now they're asking me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for something in return.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:42.252 --> 00:12:43.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what it is yet</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:44.371 --> 00:12:46.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm not going to return</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the tablet until I do.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:46.592 --> 00:12:49.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the key. I can feel it.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:49.940 --> 00:12:51.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you're wrong about that, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:52.370 --> 00:12:53.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have you got?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:53.490 --> 00:12:55.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer has translated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>part of the inscription.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:55.688 --> 00:12:58.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It probably lacks the eloquence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the original passage</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:12:58.029 --> 00:12:59.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you'll get the gist of it.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:00.748 --> 00:13:02.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here it is in modern Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:04.107 --> 00:13:06.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: "The time of Reckoning is at hand.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:08.244 --> 00:13:09.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"The Prophets will weep.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:13:10.784 --> 00:13:12.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Their sorrow will consume...</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:13:16.861 --> 00:13:19.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Gateway to the Temple."</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:22.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me I'm wrong...</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:13:24.379 --> 00:13:26.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but isn't the Gateway</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Temple Deep Space Nine?</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:13:37.975 --> 00:13:39.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just telling you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what the translation said.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:13:39.837 --> 00:13:41.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did not say I believed it.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:13:41.414 --> 00:13:42.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm not worried.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:13:42.914 --> 00:13:44.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you look hard enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll find a Bajoran prophecy</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:44.976 --> 00:13:45.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for just about anything.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:45.893 --> 00:13:48.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ancient texts are a tangle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of vague contradictions.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:48.795 --> 00:13:50.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, this one is anything but vague</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:13:50.655 --> 00:13:53.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and Bajoran prophecies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have an odd way of coming true.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:13:53.345 --> 00:13:54.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't say you believe in this stuff, too?</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:13:54.985 --> 00:13:56.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo believes in preparing for the worst.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:13:57.064 --> 00:13:58.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>True.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:13:58.144 --> 00:14:00.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's as bad as the Bajorans.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:14:01.088 --> 00:14:03.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Business hasn't been this slow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since the Dominion was here.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:05.207 --> 00:14:07.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I feel I have a civic duty</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:14:07.629 --> 00:14:09.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to do something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about all this doom and gloom</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:14:09.666 --> 00:14:12.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which is why I want to tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I've extended happy hour.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:14:12.426 --> 00:14:13.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Extended it?</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:14.204 --> 00:14:16.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From now on, every hour is happy hour...</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:14:17.066 --> 00:14:18.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at least until business picks up.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:14:18.984 --> 00:14:20.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eat, drink, and be merry.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:20.802 --> 00:14:22.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For tomorrow, we die.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:23.842 --> 00:14:26.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what does the Captain say about this?</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:26.641 --> 00:14:27.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is reserving judgment</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:27.782 --> 00:14:29.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>until the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has finished the translation.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:30.119 --> 00:14:32.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who knows? The rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the tablet probably says</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:32.459 --> 00:14:34.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Go to Quark's. It's happy hour."</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:34.338 --> 00:14:35.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like the way you think, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:35.738 --> 00:14:38.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, this is ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing's going to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:14:38.497 --> 00:14:40.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someday, we're all going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to look back on this and laugh.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:14:41.416 --> 00:14:43.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:14:44.175 --> 00:14:45.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: What was that?</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:14:57.491 --> 00:14:59.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:15:01.990 --> 00:15:03.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did that prophecy go again?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:15:08.750 --> 00:15:10.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: You don't have to do this, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:15:10.630 --> 00:15:12.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Don't have to do what?</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:15:13.248 --> 00:15:14.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sit here, watch me eat.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:15:16.066 --> 00:15:18.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't mind.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>In fact, I rather enjoy it.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:15:19.285 --> 00:15:20.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You eat with such gusto...</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:15:22.545 --> 00:15:23.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>most of the time.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:15:24.264 --> 00:15:25.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not today.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:15:28.583 --> 00:15:30.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just wish that we knew more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Reckoning.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:30.862 --> 00:15:34.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It would give us a better idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of what the Prophets want from us.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:34.900 --> 00:15:38.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to me that, if the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:38.363 --> 00:15:40.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>want the Bajoran people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to follow a given path</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:40.573 --> 00:15:43.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they should provide</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more specific directions.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:44.452 --> 00:15:45.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't work like that.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:46.117 --> 00:15:47.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe it should.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:47.957 --> 00:15:50.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Kai would say that you lack faith.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:15:51.288 --> 00:15:52.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you would agree.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:15:54.296 --> 00:15:56.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just don't know how people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make it through the day without it.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:15:58.293 --> 00:15:58.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We manage.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:16:00.573 --> 00:16:02.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, I do have faith in some things.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:16:03.052 --> 00:16:04.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling ) Such as?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:16:04.771 --> 00:16:05.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:09.410 --> 00:16:11.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll try not to disappoint you.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:15.436 --> 00:16:17.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No doubt you've heard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the latest news from Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:18.447 --> 00:16:20.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>About the flooding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Rakantha Province, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:16:22.606 --> 00:16:26.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was also an earthquake</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Kendra Valley last night.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:16:26.944 --> 00:16:29.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This morning, a tornado struck Tamulna.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:30.913 --> 00:16:32.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our sensors indicate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that Bajor has been affected</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:32.869 --> 00:16:34.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>by the instability of the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:34.642 --> 00:16:35.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How comforting.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:36.383 --> 00:16:38.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me, do your sensors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have an explanation</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:16:38.984 --> 00:16:40.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for the instability itself?</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:16:42.183 --> 00:16:43.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:16:43.740 --> 00:16:45.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I'll give you one.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:16:46.618 --> 00:16:49.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've angered the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by taking the tablet from Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:16:50.539 --> 00:16:52.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As the spiritual leader</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Bajoran people</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:16:52.917 --> 00:16:54.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you to return it.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:16:55.576 --> 00:16:57.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And as the Emissary of the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:16:57.396 --> 00:16:59.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will ask you to give me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more time to study it.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:17:00.276 --> 00:17:01.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe it is the will of the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:17:02.455 --> 00:17:03.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I disagree.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:17:04.253 --> 00:17:06.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a formal request</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the First Minister</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:06.775 --> 00:17:08.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you to turn over the relic to me.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:09.913 --> 00:17:11.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have been very persuasive.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:12.491 --> 00:17:15.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the first time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you and Shakaar have agreed on anything.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:16.949 --> 00:17:19.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you deny his request, I promise you</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:19.889 --> 00:17:23.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>it will damage relations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between Bajor and the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:30.546 --> 00:17:31.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The tablet...</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:33.065 --> 00:17:35.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be on its way to Bajor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the morning transport.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:35.744 --> 00:17:36.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( places padd on desk )</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:17:41.722 --> 00:17:42.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As will I.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:49.860 --> 00:17:52.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're sending it back?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And I was just starting to have fun.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:53.019 --> 00:17:56.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not letting you off the hook, old man.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I need these inscriptions translated.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:17:57.379 --> 00:18:00.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can work off the holo-recordings</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I took yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:18:00.337 --> 00:18:01.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you made any more progress?</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:03.075 --> 00:18:03.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good news or bad?</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:04.115 --> 00:18:05.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On what?</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:05.576 --> 00:18:07.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On what this ideogram means.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:07.298 --> 00:18:09.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer has given me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>two possibilities.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:18:09.258 --> 00:18:09.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are?</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:10.914 --> 00:18:11.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>During the Reckoning</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:12.174 --> 00:18:14.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Bajorans will either "suffer horribly"</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:18:14.579 --> 00:18:16.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or "eat fruit."</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:18:17.892 --> 00:18:18.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Eat fruit"?</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:18:20.971 --> 00:18:23.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Given the tone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the rest of the inscriptions</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:18:24.809 --> 00:18:26.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would bet on horrible suffering.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:18:27.129 --> 00:18:27.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else do you have?</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:18:28.689 --> 00:18:31.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll love this. It's about you.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:18:32.408 --> 00:18:35.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Once the Reckoning begins,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Emissary will..."</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:18:36.727 --> 00:18:37.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:18:37.727 --> 00:18:38.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping you could tell me.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:18:39.845 --> 00:18:41.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the rest of the</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inscription's damaged.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:18:42.084 --> 00:18:43.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that figures.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:18:43.604 --> 00:18:45.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:18:45.784 --> 00:18:47.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I wish the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would stop doing that.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:18:47.783 --> 00:18:49.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do I. Keep at it, old man.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:18:49.664 --> 00:18:50.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just do me one favor.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:18:51.302 --> 00:18:54.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you talk to the Prophets again</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ask for a dictionary...</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:18:55.540 --> 00:18:56.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>please.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:18:56.682 --> 00:18:57.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see what I can do.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:18:58.640 --> 00:18:59.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:06.077 --> 00:19:08.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, I have a message for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from General Martok.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:09.076 --> 00:19:09.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:19:10.157 --> 00:19:12.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's dispatched</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three Klingon attack cruisers</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:19:12.238 --> 00:19:14.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to bolster the defense perimeter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the Dorala system.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:19:15.115 --> 00:19:18.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good. I just hope they can hold out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until Starfleet sends in reinforcements.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:19:19.314 --> 00:19:21.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons will hold out.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Martok will see to it.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:19:25.672 --> 00:19:26.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Long day?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:19:27.292 --> 00:19:28.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They seem to get longer.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:19:29.531 --> 00:19:31.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll feel better in the morning...</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:19:31.930 --> 00:19:34.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>once the Kai is off the station.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:19:34.280 --> 00:19:35.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:19:35.555 --> 00:19:38.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She may be the spiritual leader</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of millions of Bajorans</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:19:38.137 --> 00:19:40.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but she is not an easy woman to like.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:19:40.547 --> 00:19:43.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if it's any comfort</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think she likes you, either.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:19:43.526 --> 00:19:44.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've known that for a while.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:19:45.466 --> 00:19:46.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess I should have consulted her</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:19:46.706 --> 00:19:48.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before I brought the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>up to the station.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:19:49.485 --> 00:19:50.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She would have tried to stop you.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:19:51.245 --> 00:19:53.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah... that's why I didn't ask her.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:19:53.884 --> 00:19:55.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a way, I feel sorry for her.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:19:55.643 --> 00:19:58.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She spends her whole life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in service to the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:19:58.922 --> 00:20:02.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then one day, after years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of self-sacrifice and commitment</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:20:02.864 --> 00:20:04.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>she gets her reward. She's elected Kai.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:20:05.887 --> 00:20:07.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Should've been the greatest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>moment of her life.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:20:09.937 --> 00:20:12.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But my being the Emissary</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>spoiled it for her.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:20:12.539 --> 00:20:15.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, the Kai's always been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the spiritual leader of Bajor</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:20:16.117 --> 00:20:18.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Winn has to share that role with you</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:20:18.295 --> 00:20:19.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to make matters worse</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:20:19.895 --> 00:20:21.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're an outsider, a non-Bajoran.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:20:21.755 --> 00:20:23.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she can never forgive you for.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:20:23.874 --> 00:20:26.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's why she made</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>such an issue of the whole thing.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:20:27.074 --> 00:20:28.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, she's jealous of you</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:20:28.793 --> 00:20:31.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and of your relationship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:20:32.632 --> 00:20:34.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm a little envious myself.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:20:34.232 --> 00:20:35.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:20:36.591 --> 00:20:38.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You speak with the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:20:38.412 --> 00:20:39.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They listen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:20:39.812 --> 00:20:41.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's...</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:20:41.091 --> 00:20:42.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that's a rare gift.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:20:43.529 --> 00:20:44.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Certainly nothing I asked for.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:20:45.449 --> 00:20:49.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's why I don't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>resent you, but the Kai does.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:20:51.476 --> 00:20:52.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll keep that in mind.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:21:06.192 --> 00:21:07.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong, Eminence?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:21:09.741 --> 00:21:11.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you say that, child?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:21:11.388 --> 00:21:12.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem troubled.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:21:12.660 --> 00:21:13.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:21:14.459 --> 00:21:15.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am quite relieved</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:17.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Emissary has decided</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to do the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:21:18.724 --> 00:21:19.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you didn't leave him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>much choice, did you?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:21:21.437 --> 00:21:24.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I enjoyed forcing his hand.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:21:25.797 --> 00:21:28.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assure you, I did not.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:21:28.556 --> 00:21:32.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish the situation had been resolved</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more amicably.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:21:32.514 --> 00:21:34.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps the next time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have a disagreement</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:21:34.793 --> 00:21:36.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'll consider my wishes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more thoughtfully.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:21:37.112 --> 00:21:38.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next time?</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:21:38.112 --> 00:21:39.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're anticipating more disagreements?</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:21:41.732 --> 00:21:44.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I merely meant to express</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my hope that, in the future</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:21:44.553 --> 00:21:46.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we can work together</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the good of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:21:47.109 --> 00:21:47.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:21:48.068 --> 00:21:50.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, you are on the same side,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aren't you?</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:21:51.029 --> 00:21:51.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Naturally.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:21:52.848 --> 00:21:54.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:21:54.947 --> 00:21:56.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no higher calling.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:22:00.948 --> 00:22:03.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( deep rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:22:05.927 --> 00:22:07.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:22:07.143 --> 00:22:08.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:22:08.103 --> 00:22:08.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:22:10.917 --> 00:22:11.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake-o.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:22:19.289 --> 00:22:19.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're up late.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:22:20.260 --> 00:22:21.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so are you.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:22:21.899 --> 00:22:22.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's on your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:22:24.259 --> 00:22:26.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know. I guess I just wanted to see</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you're all right.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:22:28.257 --> 00:22:29.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:22:29.617 --> 00:22:31.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Since when did you become a worrier?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:22:33.656 --> 00:22:35.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:22:35.157 --> 00:22:36.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's this Emissary stuff.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:22:38.094 --> 00:22:39.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It scares me a little.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:22:46.532 --> 00:22:47.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twice now...</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:22:48.012 --> 00:22:49.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>twice in one year...</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:22:50.611 --> 00:22:52.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir's called me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>down to the Infirmary</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:22:52.810 --> 00:22:54.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to tell me something was wrong with you</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:22:55.289 --> 00:22:56.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there you were</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:22:57.568 --> 00:23:00.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>lying unconscious on a bio-bed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>having visions or something.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:23:02.647 --> 00:23:03.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And there...</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:23:03.766 --> 00:23:05.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all I could do was just stand there</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:23:06.966 --> 00:23:08.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and, and wonder...</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:23:09.245 --> 00:23:10.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>if you were ever going to wake up.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:23:13.804 --> 00:23:16.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it hasn't been easy, Jake.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:23:16.803 --> 00:23:18.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want it to happen again.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:23:22.541 --> 00:23:26.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, I didn't ask</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be the Emissary...</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:31.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, for better or worse,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I guess that's what I am...</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:23:34.678 --> 00:23:36.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>except for being your dad.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:24:20.144 --> 00:24:24.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do you always have to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so damned mysterious?</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:24:26.982 --> 00:24:28.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Answer me.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:24:30.121 --> 00:24:31.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am tired of your riddles!</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:24:33.560 --> 00:24:36.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you need me to do, say so!</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:24:41.238 --> 00:24:42.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:25:10.271 --> 00:25:11.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me guess.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:25:12.108 --> 00:25:13.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You accidentally knocked it over.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:25:15.271 --> 00:25:15.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:25:16.313 --> 00:25:17.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think so.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:25:17.495 --> 00:25:19.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what did happen?</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:25:21.058 --> 00:25:23.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just had this uncontrollable urge</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:25:24.217 --> 00:25:25.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to smash the tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:25:26.097 --> 00:25:27.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I get those urges all the time.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:25:28.455 --> 00:25:30.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, I never act on them.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:25:32.495 --> 00:25:35.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not reading</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any residual energy signatures.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:25:35.634 --> 00:25:38.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's impossible.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Check the station's internal sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:25:40.912 --> 00:25:42.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:25:42.174 --> 00:25:43.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I tell you, I saw something.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:25:43.714 --> 00:25:45.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We believe you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:25:45.036 --> 00:25:47.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, please, Constable, don't patronize me.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:25:51.821 --> 00:25:52.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sisko to Ops. Report.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:25:53.181 --> 00:25:55.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We just experienced</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a station-wide power drain.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:25:55.664 --> 00:25:57.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're attempting to determine the source.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:25:57.415 --> 00:25:58.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep me informed.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:25:58.415 --> 00:26:00.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Aye, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

455
00:26:00.167 --> 00:26:05.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's possible the power drain is related</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to this energy discharge you saw.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:26:06.485 --> 00:26:08.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm starting to think the same thing.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:26:10.403 --> 00:26:13.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, you're not getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another urge, are you?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:26:14.242 --> 00:26:15.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:26:17.912 --> 00:26:19.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've done what I needed to do.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:26:21.368 --> 00:26:23.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this might sound strange</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:26:24.640 --> 00:26:27.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I think the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted me to shatter the tablet.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:26:27.963 --> 00:26:29.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Try explaining that to Kai Winn.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:26:30.754 --> 00:26:33.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe that you'd be so petty</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:26:33.035 --> 00:26:35.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>as to destroy the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>rather than turn it over to me.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:26:36.363 --> 00:26:37.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not why I did it.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:26:38.923 --> 00:26:41.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the Prophets wanted you</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:26:41.781 --> 00:26:45.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy a priceless piece</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Bajor's history?</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:26:46.105 --> 00:26:47.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's exactly what you have to believe.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:26:48.828 --> 00:26:50.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And why would they do that?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:26:50.739 --> 00:26:52.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I had an answer for you.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:26:53.060 --> 00:26:54.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm sure you'll</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>come up with something.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:26:58.138 --> 00:27:01.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and I haven't always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seen things eye to eye</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:27:01.336 --> 00:27:02.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but we have one thing in common--</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:27:02.889 --> 00:27:05.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we both believe that the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have a plan for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:27:05.610 --> 00:27:08.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, sometimes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's not easy to see the path</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:27:08.913 --> 00:27:09.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>they've laid out for us.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:27:11.373 --> 00:27:14.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right now, I don't know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what they want from me</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:27:15.413 --> 00:27:18.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm willing to take a leap of faith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and trust that they're guiding me</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:27:18.115 --> 00:27:20.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm asking you to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>take that leap with me.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:27:20.794 --> 00:27:23.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a leap of faith, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:27:23.953 --> 00:27:26.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets have made it quite clear.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:27:26.832 --> 00:27:30.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two-thirds of the Rakantha wheat harvest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have been destroyed by floods.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:27:30.952 --> 00:27:33.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Earthquakes have devastated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kendra Province</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:27:33.780 --> 00:27:34.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>leaving hundreds homeless.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:27:35.978 --> 00:27:38.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajorans are suffering because of you.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:27:38.765 --> 00:27:41.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're paying the price</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your act of sacrilege.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:27:44.603 --> 00:27:46.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Captain Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

488
00:27:47.070 --> 00:27:48.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:27:48.389 --> 00:27:50.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> You'd better come down</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to the Promenade, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

490
00:27:50.668 --> 00:27:51.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there a problem?</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:27:51.727 --> 00:27:52.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> I'll let you be the judge of that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:28:05.319 --> 00:28:07.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think we've found the source</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the power fluctuations.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:28:08.587 --> 00:28:10.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I tried to talk to her,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she ignored me.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:28:16.973 --> 00:28:18.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind whistling )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:28:18.813 --> 00:28:20.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( glass exploding )</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:28:34.248 --> 00:28:37.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( voice reverberating) You...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are the Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:28:39.226 --> 00:28:40.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep your hands off your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:28:41.498 --> 00:28:42.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a Prophet.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:28:44.160 --> 00:28:45.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why have you taken this woman's body?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:28:47.039 --> 00:28:48.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This vessel is willing.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:28:50.718 --> 00:28:51.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Reckoning...</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:28:53.237 --> 00:28:54.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it is time.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:29:02.325 --> 00:29:04.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The Reckoning... what is it?</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:29:04.604 --> 00:29:05.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The end...</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:29:06.564 --> 00:29:07.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:29:08.284 --> 00:29:09.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:29:12.203 --> 00:29:14.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await Kosst Amojan.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:29:14.242 --> 00:29:15.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Evil One.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:29:16.601 --> 00:29:20.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Pah-wraith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>banished from the Celestial Temple.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:29:21.023 --> 00:29:24.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're saying a Pah-wraith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will take corporeal form as well?</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:29:24.541 --> 00:29:26.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The battle will be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:29:26.442 --> 00:29:28.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This battle... is it to be fought here?</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:29:29.082 --> 00:29:31.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajor will be reborn.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:29:32.155 --> 00:29:33.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shabren's Fifth Prophecy--</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:29:34.769 --> 00:29:35.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Rebirth.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:29:36.388 --> 00:29:39.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the Evil One is destroyed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it will bring a thousand years of peace--</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:29:41.026 --> 00:29:43.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Golden Age of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:29:45.227 --> 00:29:46.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it is destroyed?</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:29:49.032 --> 00:29:50.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who will prevail is not known.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:29:51.054 --> 00:29:52.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want from me?</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:29:53.217 --> 00:29:54.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Am I supposed to help you in some way?</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:29:55.459 --> 00:29:59.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Sisko has completed his task.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:30:02.425 --> 00:30:03.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive my blindness.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:30:07.232 --> 00:30:08.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prophet, hear me.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:30:09.515 --> 00:30:10.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am the Kai of Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:30:11.477 --> 00:30:14.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I offer myself to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as your humble servant.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:30:15.956 --> 00:30:17.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I await their vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:30:18.397 --> 00:30:19.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Speak to me.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:30:20.019 --> 00:30:21.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what I should do.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:30:32.215 --> 00:30:33.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're evacuating.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:30:34.957 --> 00:30:35.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't be serious.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:30:36.299 --> 00:30:38.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This battle could destroy the station.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:30:38.381 --> 00:30:39.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then don't let it be fought here.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:30:40.804 --> 00:30:42.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have any choice.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:30:42.166 --> 00:30:43.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, you do.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:30:43.710 --> 00:30:46.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can flood the Promenade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with chroniton radiation.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:30:46.627 --> 00:30:48.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you suggesting that we kill a Prophet?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:30:48.889 --> 00:30:49.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:30:49.888 --> 00:30:51.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: You don't have to.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:30:51.670 --> 00:30:53.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you ramp up the chroniton levels slowly</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:30:54.493 --> 00:30:56.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you'll give the wormhole alien</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a chance to leave</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:30:56.013 --> 00:30:57.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kira's body without getting hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:30:57.325 --> 00:30:59.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: We have everything rigged</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and ready to go.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:30:59.565 --> 00:31:00.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just say the word.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:31:05.123 --> 00:31:06.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:31:06.904 --> 00:31:07.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:31:09.407 --> 00:31:12.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deep Space Nine is critical</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the defense of the Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:31:12.169 --> 00:31:13.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We cannot risk destroying it.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:31:14.112 --> 00:31:16.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Dominion fleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was about to come through the wormhole</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:31:17.464 --> 00:31:18.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked the Prophets for their help.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:31:19.317 --> 00:31:20.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:31:20.879 --> 00:31:22.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now they're asking for my help.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:31:23.302 --> 00:31:25.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They need to fight this battle here, now.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:31:25.804 --> 00:31:27.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to jeopardize my crew</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:31:29.008 --> 00:31:31.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm not going to stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the way of the Prophets, either.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:31:31.630 --> 00:31:32.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if the Prophets lose?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:31:32.791 --> 00:31:34.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you willing to sacrifice Kira?</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:31:35.801 --> 00:31:38.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophet said she was willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:31:38.904 --> 00:31:39.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:31:40.224 --> 00:31:41.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:31:44.554 --> 00:31:46.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know how important</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>her faith is to her and...</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:31:47.857 --> 00:31:50.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no doubt that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she would allow the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:31:50.399 --> 00:31:52.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to use her as their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:31:56.011 --> 00:31:58.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll notify Starfleet that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're abandoning the station.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:32:00.495 --> 00:32:02.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Begin the evacuation immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:32:14.251 --> 00:32:16.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Hurry along, now. Hurry along.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:32:17.090 --> 00:32:18.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is this transport full?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-There's room.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:32:18.630 --> 00:32:20.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to check the</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Promenade for stragglers.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:32:21.133 --> 00:32:24.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo, you should've helped us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>persuade the Captain to end this.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:32:25.416 --> 00:32:26.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to respect Kira's wishes.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:32:27.679 --> 00:32:29.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it were Dax, I am not sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I could've done the same.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:32:29.941 --> 00:32:32.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, just be grateful</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you didn't have to make that choice.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:32:33.985 --> 00:32:36.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For your sake, I hope</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets are victorious.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:32:36.968 --> 00:32:39.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They will be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if Kira has anything to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:32:42.126 --> 00:32:43.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:32:45.725 --> 00:32:46.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Report.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:32:46.885 --> 00:32:49.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We expect to be down to a skeleton crew</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>within the hour.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:32:49.004 --> 00:32:49.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very well.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:32:50.227 --> 00:32:51.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did Starfleet have to say?</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:32:52.029 --> 00:32:53.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I managed to convince them</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:32:53.190 --> 00:32:55.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that we couldn't afford</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to defy the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:32:56.257 --> 00:32:57.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>WORF: They are the only thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's keeping the Dominion</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:32:57.024 --> 00:32:58.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:32:58.744 --> 00:33:02.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only problem is, there's no guarantee</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets will win this battle.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:33:02.264 --> 00:33:03.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>

586
00:33:03.415 --> 00:33:04.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Constable.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:33:04.898 --> 00:33:06.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Captain, there's a group of Bajorans</i></c.bg_transparent>

588
00:33:06.258 --> 00:33:08.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>on the Promenade</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>who are refusing to leave.</i></c.bg_transparent>

589
00:33:10.254 --> 00:33:15.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WINN:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Tera dak embah</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ihsehelm ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

590
00:33:15.573 --> 00:33:17.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ALL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>de-ram ta-meen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

591
00:33:19.332 --> 00:33:21.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tera dak ihsehelm</i></c.bg_transparent>

592
00:33:21.371 --> 00:33:22.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

593
00:33:23.371 --> 00:33:24.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ALL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>de-ram ta-meen...</i></c.bg_transparent>

594
00:33:25.511 --> 00:33:27.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last transports are standing by.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:33:28.151 --> 00:33:31.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>WINN:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Tera dak ihsehelm</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ran embah...</i></c.bg_transparent>

596
00:33:32.149 --> 00:33:33.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eminence.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:33:33.189 --> 00:33:34.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>...ta-meen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

598
00:33:36.788 --> 00:33:37.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:33:37.830 --> 00:33:38.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>These people have to go.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:33:40.531 --> 00:33:42.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're offering prayers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the Prophets' victory.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:33:43.514 --> 00:33:45.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will hear your prayers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wherever you are.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:33:45.917 --> 00:33:47.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It isn't safe here.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:33:48.660 --> 00:33:50.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why are you still here, Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:33:51.422 --> 00:33:53.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophet told you your task was done.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:33:54.405 --> 00:33:56.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am Captain of this station</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:33:56.068 --> 00:33:58.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I will do everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in my power to save it.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:33:58.548 --> 00:34:01.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, are you going to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tell these people to go</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:34:01.388 --> 00:34:02.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or shall I?</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:34:07.571 --> 00:34:08.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My children</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:34:08.891 --> 00:34:10.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets have heard your prayers.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:34:10.851 --> 00:34:12.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must go.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:34:16.329 --> 00:34:17.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take them to the transports.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:34:20.367 --> 00:34:21.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, this way.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:34:21.967 --> 00:34:24.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Congratulations, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:34:24.467 --> 00:34:26.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks to you the Prophets'</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>victory is at hand.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:34:27.250 --> 00:34:28.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you're right.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:34:29.170 --> 00:34:31.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is your faith, Emissary?</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:34:31.271 --> 00:34:33.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't think the Evil One</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be victorious, do you?</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:34:35.475 --> 00:34:38.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rest assured, the Golden Age is upon us.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:34:39.539 --> 00:34:42.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets and the people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be as one.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:34:43.362 --> 00:34:44.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:34:44.399 --> 00:34:46.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There will be no need for vedeks or kais</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:34:48.230 --> 00:34:49.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or even Emissaries.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:34:53.148 --> 00:34:55.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kosst Amojan has chosen its vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:35:07.462 --> 00:35:08.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let it begin.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:35:17.690 --> 00:35:19.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave my son and take me instead!</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:35:21.974 --> 00:35:23.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your Emissary offers himself to us.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:35:25.437 --> 00:35:26.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His faith wavers.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:35:28.235 --> 00:35:29.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:35:39.592 --> 00:35:41.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:36:05.864 --> 00:36:07.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Emissary, we must go.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:36:18.732 --> 00:36:20.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, Worf is standing by in Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:36:20.835 --> 00:36:23.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He can trigger the chroniton generator</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at your command.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:36:23.235 --> 00:36:24.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can still end this, Ben.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:36:24.397 --> 00:36:25.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I've got to play this thing out.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:36:26.278 --> 00:36:27.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is your son out there.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:36:27.285 --> 00:36:29.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you think I know that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will protect him.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:36:30.686 --> 00:36:32.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're trying to kill him.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:36:32.659 --> 00:36:34.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. They're trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to destroy the Pah-wraith.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:36:34.687 --> 00:36:37.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets will not let</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anything happen to him.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:36:37.330 --> 00:36:38.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know that?</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:36:38.569 --> 00:36:39.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:36:41.633 --> 00:36:42.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to get out of here.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:36:42.975 --> 00:36:44.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to the sensors,</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:36:44.196 --> 00:36:47.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the energy building between them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could explode at any second.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:36:47.520 --> 00:36:48.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to leave Jake here.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:36:50.803 --> 00:36:52.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We must go, Emissary.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:36:52.645 --> 00:36:53.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin...</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:36:53.685 --> 00:36:56.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get out of here!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get off the station, both of you!</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:36:56.364 --> 00:36:57.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an order!</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:36:57.363 --> 00:36:58.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come, child. We must go.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:37:07.200 --> 00:37:08.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax to Worf.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:37:12.065 --> 00:37:12.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:37:13.145 --> 00:37:15.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Meet me at Airlock Eight. We're leaving.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:37:19.103 --> 00:37:21.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on ahead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Airlock Eight is down to the right.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:37:22.262 --> 00:37:24.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This way. Move quickly.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:37:24.662 --> 00:37:26.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go. Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:37:26.701 --> 00:37:27.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hurry up.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:37:27.821 --> 00:37:29.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's okay, it's okay.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:37:29.980 --> 00:37:31.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think the transport is down here.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:37:55.732 --> 00:37:57.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No!</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:37:58.571 --> 00:38:01.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chroniton levels at 37% and rising.</i></c.bg_transparent>

663
00:38:03.332 --> 00:38:04.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May the Prophets forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:38:28.364 --> 00:38:29.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake...</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:38:37.921 --> 00:38:39.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's Log, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

666
00:38:40.203 --> 00:38:43.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The station's population</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>has returned</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and repairs are underway.</i></c.bg_transparent>

667
00:38:44.146 --> 00:38:46.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Major Kira has recovered</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>from her experience...</i></c.bg_transparent>

668
00:38:46.969 --> 00:38:49.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but my son is still</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>in the Infirmary.</i></c.bg_transparent>

669
00:38:51.168 --> 00:38:52.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake?</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:38:52.207 --> 00:38:54.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be, uh, laid up for a few days</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but he'll be all right.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:38:55.166 --> 00:38:56.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I see him?</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:38:56.167 --> 00:38:57.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, yes.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:39:04.723 --> 00:39:05.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jake...</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:39:08.962 --> 00:39:10.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dad.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:39:10.285 --> 00:39:11.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:39:12.657 --> 00:39:13.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Could be worse.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:39:16.524 --> 00:39:17.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be up and about in no time.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:39:21.278 --> 00:39:22.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to say.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:39:24.396 --> 00:39:26.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Say you're happy to see me.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:39:27.276 --> 00:39:28.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know I am.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:39:30.995 --> 00:39:32.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I...</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:39:34.738 --> 00:39:36.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to explain what happened...</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:39:38.655 --> 00:39:40.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'm not sure that I can.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:39:42.454 --> 00:39:43.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't have to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:39:45.396 --> 00:39:47.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Pah-wraith was inside me</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:39:48.779 --> 00:39:50.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could feel its hatred</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:39:51.290 --> 00:39:54.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I knew that no matter what</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:39:55.034 --> 00:39:56.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it couldn't be allowed to win...</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:39:59.887 --> 00:40:00.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>even if it meant I had to die.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:40:03.778 --> 00:40:05.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:40:18.701 --> 00:40:19.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was the prayer service?</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:40:20.343 --> 00:40:22.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To tell you the truth</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't pay that much attention.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:40:22.862 --> 00:40:25.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still trying to make sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of everything that happened.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:40:25.262 --> 00:40:29.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, of all the people on this station</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Prophets chose me.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:40:29.661 --> 00:40:33.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I know why</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve that honor.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:40:33.542 --> 00:40:36.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps that's why you were chosen.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You have faith and humility.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:40:36.404 --> 00:40:38.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard that you told the Captain</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:40:38.606 --> 00:40:40.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that I was willing to give my life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:40:42.180 --> 00:40:44.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate that you respect my beliefs.</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:40:45.483 --> 00:40:49.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just the same, I wouldn't have minded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if the Prophets had chosen someone else.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:40:52.520 --> 00:40:53.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to go.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:40:53.920 --> 00:40:56.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll drop by Security</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after I take the Kai to her shuttle.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:41:06.316 --> 00:41:08.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary couldn't escort me himself?</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:41:09.356 --> 00:41:10.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's with his son.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:41:11.018 --> 00:41:12.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would think he'd want to thank me.</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:41:13.177 --> 00:41:14.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For what?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:41:14.978 --> 00:41:17.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I prevented the destruction</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:41:17.941 --> 00:41:21.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saved the Emissary's life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the life of his son.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:41:21.964 --> 00:41:23.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't pretend you did it for the Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:41:24.807 --> 00:41:26.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did it for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:41:26.610 --> 00:41:29.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you haven't heard,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the floodwaters have receded</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:41:29.809 --> 00:41:31.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the earthquakes have stopped.</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:41:31.529 --> 00:41:33.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you're going to take credit for that?</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:41:35.010 --> 00:41:37.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it as a sign I did the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:41:37.412 --> 00:41:39.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You defied the will of the Prophets</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:41:39.415 --> 00:41:40.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and you did it</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:41:40.877 --> 00:41:44.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you couldn't stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the fact that a human, an infidel,</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:41:45.361 --> 00:41:46.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>had a stronger faith than you.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:41:47.471 --> 00:41:50.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Emissary was willing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to sacrifice his own son</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:41:50.213 --> 00:41:51.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to serve the Prophets.</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:41:52.216 --> 00:41:54.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My faith is as pure as the Emissary's.</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:41:56.300 --> 00:41:59.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you're confusing faith</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with ambition.</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:42:00.283 --> 00:42:03.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not confusing anything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>child, you are.</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:42:03.987 --> 00:42:06.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Prophets chose you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as their instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:42:06.970 --> 00:42:09.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't mean you can speak for them.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:42:10.351 --> 00:42:13.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because of your interference,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Reckoning was stopped.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:42:13.634 --> 00:42:15.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The evil still exists.</c.bg_transparent>

728
00:42:16.317 --> 00:42:19.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm not sure if even the Prophets know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what that will mean for Bajor.</c.bg_transparent>

